The project objectives are:
 Establish an evolved manager notes that will be used at the service level education;
 Provide support to an academic registration;
 To allow monitoring of students' grades and know at any moment the state of the student;
 Capitalize history to provide output states:
 Certificate of Registration
 Certificate of education
 Transcripts
 Certificate of Achievement
 A system of student research;
 Have a system access control functions and roles to users;
 Provide an easy interface and secure access to all its users;
 Generate minutes of deliberations etdes modules by collecting these grades.
 Having statistics by age, city, gender, region, the degree of validation of students for each module, each semester, every branch, every year things that can help managers make decisions and future changes at all levels.
